ca.uhn.hl7v2.model.v25.message

Class MFN_Znn

  • java.lang.Object
    • ca.uhn.hl7v2.model.AbstractStructure
      • ca.uhn.hl7v2.model.AbstractGroup
        • ca.uhn.hl7v2.model.AbstractMessage
          • ca.uhn.hl7v2.model.v25.message.MFN_Znn
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Group, Message, Structure, Visitable, Serializable

    public class MFN_Znn
extends AbstractMessage

    Represents a MFN_Znn message structure (see chapter 8.4.3). This structure contains the following elements:

    • 1: MSH (Message Header)
    • 2: SFT (Software Segment) optional repeating
    • 3: MFI (Master File Identification)
    • 4: MFN_Znn_MF_SITE_DEFINED (a Group object) repeating
    See Also:
    Serialized Form
